[FILE:282:descriptions/desc.primary]
GtkSourceView is a portable C library that extends the standard GTK
framework for multiline text editing with support for configurable
syntax highlighting, unlimited undo/redo, search and replace, a
completion framework, printing and other features typical of a
source code editor.


